(1924, 280, 'about_me_text', 'I\'m a Front-End Web Developer in Vancouver, BC. Inspired to make a change from my career in Tourism, I began my coding journey at BCIT where I was hooked from my first Hello World! I\'ve always enjoyed writing and transferred that knack to computer languages. What excites me most about life is travelling, experiencing different cultures and cuisines, losing myself in nature, and continually learning something new. I\'ve always felt a connection to animals and nature and care deeply about animal welfare and sustainability. I believe that if it doesn\'t challenge you, it doesn\'t change you and life is all about change.'),
